title: Park Shin Hye greets fans while filming in Thailand | allkpop.com
text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Park Shin Hye greets fans while filming in Thailand By KpopJoA 10 minutes ago 2,584 431 0 0 Google+ On February 17, actress Park Shin Hye gave a warm greeting to fans from Thailand by posting through her Instagram page.
"I am currently filming in Thailand surrounded by a garden of daffodils for brand ' Mamonde' . Thank you to all the fans who came out to see me at the airport yesterday. I was shocked to see everyone since it was so late at night, thank you so much." 
The actress is glowing, giving the victory sign admiring nature for an outdoor photo shoot.
